      "span_text": "High resolution MRI was used to confirm the clinical finding of generally reduced movement in the bones of the hindfoot after surgical treatment of CTEV.  It was noted that the movement of the individual bones in the hindfoot was not only less in magnitude after surgery but also sometimes occurred in a completely different direction to the normal."
